HEADWORD: Pining
<hw>Pin"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Languishing; drooping; wasting away, as with longing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Wasting; consuming.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>pining</xex> malady of France.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Piningly</ent>⟦br⟧
